##################
#    FIREFOX     #
##################

a big problem in firefox with dark themes is that the text is unreadable, 
to fix it  you need to do this:

install stylish from
https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/stylish/

Go to
 Tools > Add-ons > User styles > Write new style

see: http://www.mediafire.com/view/?nzlfspuydo49n#hgsaetjxac4h8p1


then copy and paste this code:

...........................................

  html input[type="text"],
  html input[type="password"],
  html textarea {
      color: #202020 !important;
      background: white !important;
  }

...........................................

and save it, you can use any name for this style

see: http://www.mediafire.com/view/?nzlfspuydo49n#2rh2lt2tdggc7u3

Restart Firefox

now enjoy


